As in some other cases involving taxa (e.g.,
Alyssum muelleri , Lepidium intricatum
) that were collected by Buhse in 1849 and described jointly with Boissier ( BOISSIER & BUHSE, 1860 ), pre-printed 1847 labels were used by Boissier and to which he added some or all collection data. Therefore, the specimens of such collections in G-BOIS are considered duplicates of the same collections at LE that have the full and correct collection information in the protologues of those taxa.
